# .gitignore — Android-to-webOS-Ports
#
# This repo is the PORTING FRAMEWORK, toolkit, and docs ONLY — the apkenv-based
# shim source, build/packaging scripts, per-game modules, and the methodology.
# It must contain NO game code or copyrighted game content: this is a
# bring-your-own-apk toolkit (ship the porter, not the games).
#
# Patterns are written WITHOUT a leading slash (or with **/) so they match at any
# depth — the toolkit source lives under apkenv/, a subdirectory.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Game code & copyrighted content — NEVER COMMIT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Android game packages (candidates, working copies, anything) — but keep the
# android-candidates/ folder + its README (drop-your-donor-apks-here marker).
*.apk
# Built webOS packages — the .ipk BUNDLES the game apk, so it is game content too
*.ipk
# Extracted / patched game engine binaries
libwmw*.so
libfmodex*.so
wmw-patch/
# Extracted game asset trees
gameroot/
# Game imagery (launcher icons & screenshots contain copyrighted game art)
SDL_*.png
**/packaging/webos/icon.png
**/packaging/.icontmp/
# Packaging staging/output (assembled from the game apk + harvested libs)
**/packaging/out/
**/packaging/stage/
**/packaging/*.apk

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Proprietary / device-harvested binaries — NOT committed.
# HP's libEGL is proprietary and not in the PalmPDK SDK, so build-webos.sh
# harvests it from a connected device (novacom) into apkenv/devlibs/ at build
# time. The FOSS Android bionic runtime libs in apkenv/libs/webos/
# (libc/libm/libstdc++/liblog/libz) ARE committed — they are the porter's
# runtime payload, not device-specific.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
libEGL.so
**/devlibs/
**/staging-libs/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.o
*.d
build/
**/compat/gen/
# compiled host binaries (output of build-webos.sh)
/apkenv/apkenv
*.apkenv.so
libdvm_compat.so
hostui
dist/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Logs, cores, scratch
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.minicore
core
core.*

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Editor / OS noise
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
tags
cscope.out
*.swp
*.orig
